HOW TO BUY

Step 1: Set Up Your Wallet

Get a digital wallet (Trust Wallet or Metamask), download it from your app store if you don't have one. Add Ethereum (ETH) to the wallet, and be aware of gas/tax fees on every ETH transactions.

Step 2: Connect Wallet

Make sure you are using wallet browser. You can buy directly from Uniswap or 1inch. The steps are similar > Confirm import of $HAMSTER> Click Connect Wallet > select WalletConnect to connect.

Step 3: Swap

Now's the fun part! you should see ETH on "You Pay," and LINU on "You Receive," specify the ETH amount for HAMSTER, and view the exchanged HAMSTER amount along with gas fees. Click SWAP and Voil! you just joined the $HAMSTER community!
